snippet.title: "I Have A Baby" Amber Heard Uses Baby To Avoid Prison Sentence!
snippet.description:
Amber Heard Uses Her Recently Born Baby As An Arguing Point Not To Go To Prison!

✅ Like & Subscribe for more Celebrity Content!

Amber Heard Believes She Has Won the Battle Against Johnny Depp, and Her Career Is Safe Because of her newly adopted baby? If you've not been living under a rock for the past year, you'll notice that Johnny and Heard are at war. And things just turned to be quite interesting, as Heard now has a child to take care of and therefore "cannot go to prison" as she says. But will the baby actually have an effect on her sentence or is Oonagh Paige an irrelevant factor?

#AmberHerad #OonaghPaige #JohnnyDepp
